scopecontent.p:
Belle Dock Branch. Industrial Switching on both sides. New Haven Gas Co. plant on right;
       numerous sidings and crossovers; entrances to numerous industrial plants crossing tracks
       unprotected by lights or bells

Engineer is always on the right side. Note the many curves of the tracks. Retarders on this
       end of the classification yard are supposed to stop the cars as they roll down from the hump,
       but this does not always happen.
